        "created_at": "2016-04-08T05:00:17.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Press will certainly make you pay for it, but the wine is tempting.</p>\n<p>Working on an essay on Martha\u2019s Vineyard at the moment and that is one vintage I have never tried. Its youthfulness does not surprise however.</p>",
