        "username": "Richard_Albert",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/richard_albert/{size}/95072_2.png",
        "created_at": "2016-04-09T15:32:37.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Stan,<br>\nConsidering the greats from 1968, 1970 and 1974, Joe might have had some to sell\u2026<br>\nAll three consecutive vintages were excellent for Heitz, but the '69 has lagged behind in reception, reputation and pricing.<br>\nGlad to hear it is still going strong as are so many of the older Martha\u2019s.</p>",
